reviewText: LATINA GIRLS GOING CRAZY Volume 6 is a quite good public flashing DVD, mostly of girls in their late teens or early 20s, though a few are probably in their 30s. It was filmed on the streets (girls both on the streets and in cars) and on beaches, though it doesn't say where any of it was shot. Looks like the street scenes were possibly Miami, but do they allow topless girls on the streets there with lots of cars whizzing by? Most of the girls are very cute, but in my opinion a few scenes should have been cut - for example, a few girls don't show anything. Several girls are real knockouts, with some of them stacked, but I wonder how anyone knew that all these girls are Latinas. The nudity is almost entirely of the topless kind. Picture quality and camerawork are quite good considering the filming conditions and it's full screen 1.33:1. I like that the sound is all live, with the camera guy making humorous comments off-screen. The bonus is a decent slideshow of some of the best shots from the film. Run time is 56 minutes, plus the slide show. I'll probably get more DVDs in this "Latina Girls Going Crazy" series.
It's good to see real women showing T&A. Fat latins, Dark Latins, Old Latins, Young Latins, Light latins. I mean real latinas not some J-Lo or Silicone Barbies. Real T&A for real perverts!!!!!!
